  "intent": "Perform automated RNA extraction using magnetic bead purification on up to 16 samples. Add 4\u00b5L internal extraction control RNA to each sample, then mix with 580\u00b5L binding buffer and incubate for 5 minutes. Engage magnetic module for 6 minutes, remove supernatant, then execute sequential wash steps with wash buffer (800\u00b5L), second wash buffer (800\u00b5L), and two ethanol washes (800\u00b5L each) with 5-minute magnetic incubations between each step. Air dry beads for 10 minutes, elute RNA with 40\u00b5L nuclease-free water, incubate for 2 minutes, then transfer purified RNA to clean PCR plate.",
